      "text": "（NEXT VENUSグランプリ、決勝の朝だ）\n（とはいえ、特に変わったことはない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It’s the morning of the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix finals.)\n(But not much is different.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Morning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 8.06666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 9.489863924185434
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁ！！\nどうして芽衣がいるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Agh!\nWhat are you doing here‚ Mei?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.656530590852102,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "ノックしても返事がなかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I knocked‚ but you didn’t answer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.123197257518768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "だからって、勝手に入っていい訳じゃないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still‚ that’s no excuse to just burst in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.98986392418543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 19.223197257518777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "……麻奈ちゃん、本当にいなくなったんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ Mana really did fade away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.12319725751877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。いなくなったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. She’s gone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.723197257518777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 27.423197257518765
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、なんか落ち着いてる\n寂しくないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}… you look kinda calm.\nDon’t you miss her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.92319725751877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "うん。もちろん、寂しいといえば寂しい\nけどこれが正しい気がする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Of course I miss her.\nBut I get the feeling this is right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.35272101799648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 40.95272101799648
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "正しいって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean‚ “right”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.95272101799648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あのまま、麻奈がここにいてくれたら\nそりゃ嬉しいけど、でも、正しいことじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Mana had stayed‚\nI’d be happy‚ of course‚ but it wouldn’t be right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.32943305412928,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 51.337052018475134
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "…………うーん……\nあ！　このままだと天国に行けない幽霊さんだから？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm…\nOh! Because she’d be stuck here as a ghost forever‚ unable to go to Heaven?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.53705201847511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。そういうことかもしれない\nそれで、芽衣はどうしてここに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. That’s probably what I mean.\nSo‚ what brings you here‚ Mei?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.803718685141774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 66.97038535180843
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そうだ！　忘れてた！\n大変、リビングで大爆発！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ right! I totally forgot!\nCome quick‚ there’s been a massive explosion in the living room!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3370520184751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "はあ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2333.3333333333003,
          "startTime": 74.6333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 74.4
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 74.63333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "おい！　みんな大丈夫か！？\nなんだ？　わっ、足元にも……これ、ポップコーン？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa! Is everyone okay?!\nWhat? Agh! It’s at my feet‚ too? Wait… is this popcorn?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "どーもこーもありませんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I dread to tell you what’s happened!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "はは、さくらちゃんが手作りのポップコーン\n食べたことないって言うから、作ってたんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha… Sakura said she’d never eaten homemade popcorn before‚\nso we tried making some…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんが、入れる量間違えちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Kotono added too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……まさか、あんなに膨らむなんて\n思わなかったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had no idea it would\npuff up so much",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁー……なんだ。びっくりさせるなよ\n爆発なんて言うから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh* So that’s all? You really gave me a scare.\nYou said it was an explosion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "爆発？　何が？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Explosion? Where?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……いや、なんでもない\nそれより、みんな揃ってたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ forget it.\nAnyway‚ I didn’t know you were all here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……これから決勝を争う二つのグループとは\nとても思えないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s hard to believe that you’re in two groups about to\ncompete against each other.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "変ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it that strange?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、決勝を争う二つのグループが、その決勝当日に\nこんなに仲良くしているのは、変かもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll admit‚ to have the two groups about to compete being so chummy\non the morning of the finals… is definitely a little strange.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、確かに言われてみればそうかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true when you put it like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_20_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "でも、全然普通だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this is totally normal for us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
